This privacy notice, which will eventually be replaced by something written by a lawyer, documents your rights and ways in which your data is used.

Valour will store
- All user messages sent in the past 24 hours, subject to up to 1 hour error
- All user profile information, including your email and username which are provided to the service
- Your communities and given roles within those communities

Valour shares your data with the following third parties
- SendGrid will be provided with your email for use in mailing

By using Valour, you agree to allow us to use your data in the ways described.

You have a right to request a deletion or copy of all of your data at
support@valour.gg
